            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288217</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 推出全新 Galaxy S25 系列旗舰手机，包括 Galaxy S25、S25+ 和 S25 Ultra。设计上 S25 Ultra、S25 和 S25+ 都采用了更圆润的边角设计，提升手感之余，也让整个系列更具统一感。S25 Ultra 的边框则以钛金属制造，持机时有更高级感觉，其余型号使用铝金属边框。屏幕尺寸方面，S25、S25+ 和 S25 Ultra 分别为 6.2 吋、6.7 吋和 6.9 吋，其中 Ultra 型号荧幕边框更窄，令单手操作更加方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxys25ultrafeatur-694x355.png" alt="" width="694" height="355" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxys25ultrafeatur-694x355.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxys25ultrafeatur.png 1094w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>设计改进</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>更圆角设计</strong>：S25 Ultra、S25 和 S25+ 的设计更为统一，改用较圆角的机身，手感提升，握持更舒适。</li><li><strong>轻薄机身</strong>：荧幕增大 0.1 吋但保持与上代相似的机身尺寸，边框更窄，单手操控无压力。</li><li><strong>玻璃材质</strong>：采用更耐用的 Corning Gorilla Glass Victus 2。</li><li><strong>机身颜色</strong>：4 种钛金属色选择：黑、灰、蓝、银。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25 Ultra 荧幕尺寸为 6.9 吋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288370" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-12-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-12-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-12.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25+ 以大荧幕为卖点，其荧幕尺寸为 6.7 吋，而想要握感更实在的朋友可考虑 Galaxy S25 其荧幕尺寸为 6.2 吋</p><p style="text-align: center;"><h2>Galaxy S25 Ultra 设计特色</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08518-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08518-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08518.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Galaxy S25 Ultra 设有钛金属黑、钛金属灰、钛金属蓝及钛金属银 4 种机身颜色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288360" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另 Samsung 官方网站有提供另外三款钛金属绿色、Jetblack 以及粉金色</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288373" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-15-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-15-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-15.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288374" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-16-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-16-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-16.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-17.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25 Ultra 设计是更为纤薄、圆润的边角，令手握感觉更好</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-18-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-18.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-19-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-19-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-19.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25 Ultra 备有内置 S-Pen 轻触笔可从机身取出</p><br /><b><ul><li><strong>表格保存与分享</strong>：生成的表格可储存为图档，直接用于 Instagram 或其他社交平台的图文并茂贴文。</li></ul></li><li><strong>转置功能</strong>：用户可灵活切换表格 X/Y 轴，适应不同数据分析需求。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288316" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4.jpg 1920w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-16-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-16-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-16.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra 延续了 Ultra 系列的高规格硬件，同时专注于 Galaxy AI 功能的实用性升级，让日常操作更方便。设计更为轻薄与令操作更舒适，适合追求效能与便利的用家。</p><h2>预计发售日期与价格</h2><p>Galaxy S25 Ultra 与 S25 系列其他机款预定于 2 月 7 日上市，除了旗舰级的 S25 Ultra 起售价为 1,299 美元（约港币 HK$10,132），S25 Plus 和标准版 S25 的定价分别为 1,000 美元（约港币 HK$7,800）与 800 美元（约港币 HK$6,240）。</p><p>在 Samsung 发布香港售价后，我们也会更新上列售价。</p><h2><strong>基本规格</strong></h2><ul><li><h3>Galaxy S25 Ultra</h3><ul><li><strong>显示屏</strong>：6.9 吋 QHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X，120Hz 更新率 (1~120Hz)，Vision Booster，Adaptive Color Tone</li><li><strong>尺寸与重量</strong>：77.6 x 162.8 x 8.2 mm，218g</li><li><strong>相机</strong>：
<ul><li>50MP 超广角：F1.9, FOV 120˚</li><li>200MP 广角：OIS F1.7, FOV 85˚</li><li>50MP 长焦：5x 光学变焦, OIS F3.4, FOV 22˚</li><li>10MP 长焦：3x 光学变焦, OIS F2.4, FOV 36˚</li><li>12MP 前置：F2.2, FOV 80˚</li></ul></li><li><strong>记忆体与储存空间</strong>：12GB + 1TB / 12GB + 512GB / 12GB + 256GB</li><li><strong>电池</strong>：5,000 mAh，支援 45W 有线快充与无线充电</li><li><strong>作业系统</strong>：Android 15, One UI 7</li><li><strong>网路与连线</strong>：5G, LTE, Wi-Fi 7, Bluetooth 5.4</li><li><strong>防水防尘</strong>：IP68</li></ul><hr /><h3>Galaxy S25</h3><ul><li><strong>显示屏</strong>：6.2 吋 FHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X，120Hz 更新率 (1~120Hz)，Vision Booster，Adaptive Color Tone</li><li><strong>尺寸与重量</strong>：70.5 x 146.9 x 7.2 mm，162g</li><li><strong>相机</strong>：
