            <title>Tesla 洛杉矶餐饮充电复合站将竣工，应用程式代码透露可用 App 点餐</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/tesla-la-diner-opening/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-la-diner-opening</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/tesla-la-diner-opening/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 13:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288280</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla 在 2022 年已申请在洛杉矶兴建一个结合餐饮娱乐的超级充电站的综合项目，期望为 Tesla 车主提供便利与舒适的全新体验。最近该超级充电站综合项目竣工在即，有人在附近实拍了现场图片，另外亦有媒体在 Tesla 应用程式发现更多细节，可以预计充电站会提供餐饮娱乐服务。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">What’s round and shiny but still not yet open?<br />
Tesla diner</p><p>Lots of Supercharging stalls being installed in the adjacent lot <a href="https://t.co/Ggl5iZE205">pic.twitter.com/Ggl5iZE205</a></p><p>— AL Set (@AlSet51241438) <a href="https://twitter.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 4, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AL Set 分享的 Tesla 餐厅充电站图片，图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501">AlSet51241438@X</a></p><p>Tesla 在应用程式中新增餐厅服务功能，车主能通过手机选择餐饮服务。据《Wuangus》报道，iOS 版本最新 Tesla 应用程式代码新增了部分与餐饮有关之词汇，例如「show_diner」、「Diner Home Screen」、「profile_settings_diner_description」和「View menu &amp; amenities」，显示车主未来可透过 Tesla 应用程式查看是日餐牌，甚至可以直接从 Tesla App 点餐。由于 Tesla 知悉车主使用哪个超级充电站，因此可以预期 Tesla 餐饮充电复合站将会提供送餐服务，无须车主自行取餐。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/00_tesla_compound_re-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/00_tesla_compound_re-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/00_tesla_compound_re.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲2023 年 Tesla 展示的设计图，图片来源：<a href="https://wuangus.cc/tesla-los-angeles-restaurant-opening-soon/">Wu Angus</a></p><p>据 AL Set 分享的图片影片显示，餐厅已将近竣工，但目前 Tesla 仍未公布正式启用日期。外界期待这家餐厅成为洛杉矶电动车生态圈的新地标，推动充电设施的多元化发展，让车主在充电期间，既能享受丰富餐饮，亦可放松片刻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AL Set 分享的 Tesla 餐厅充电站图片，图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501">AlSet51241438@X</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2025/01/21/tesla-points-to-diner-integration-in-app-insurance-discount-with-full-self-driving-and-more/">Electrek</a>、<a href="https://www.teslarati.com/teslas-la-diner-and-charger-gets-closer-but-when-will-it-be-done/">Teslarati</a>、<a href="https://x.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501">AlSet51241438@X</a>、<a href="https://wuangus.cc/tesla-los-angeles-restaurant-opening-soon/">Wu Angus</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
